  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9sZWdpb25fc3ZvYm9kYS9zdGF0dXMvMTY2MDYwNjY0NTcyOTEyNDM1Mw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/legion_svoboda/status/1660606645729124353\">https://twitter.com/legion_svoboda/status/1660606645729124353</a><br/>\r\n自由俄羅斯軍團的官方推特今天（5/22）宣布他們與俄羅斯志願軍團的聯軍成功收復別爾哥羅德州的Kozinka村，同時先頭部隊已攻入格賴沃龍（Graivoron）。<br/>\r\n軍團還發了<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9sZWdpb25fc3ZvYm9kYS9zdGF0dXMvMTY2MDU1NDc2OTEyMTgxMjQ4MD90PUVGa1pKSEgyb0dHWFBLUk9sd0hHM1Emcz0xOQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/legion_svoboda/status/1660554769121812480?t=EFkZJHH2oGGXPKROlwHG3Q&amp;s=19\">這篇推文</a>宣布：「結束克里姆林宮獨裁統治的時候到了！要勇敢、不要恐懼，<b>因為我們要回家了！俄羅斯將獲得自由！</b>」<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9kZWVwc3RhdGVtYXAubGl2ZS9lbiMxMi81MC40MjU0LzM1LjYxOTM\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://deepstatemap.live/en#12/50.4254/35.6193\">https://deepstatemap.live/en#12/50.4254/35.6193</a><br/>\r\n長期關注烏俄戰爭的交互式線上地圖DeepStateMap已將該地區劃為非俄國控制。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS92aXNlZ3JhZDI0L3N0YXR1cy8xNjYwNjE3MDAxMDQ2MzQzNjgx\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/visegrad24/status/1660617001046343681\">https://twitter.com/visegrad24/status/1660617001046343681</a><br/>\r\n據稱聯軍已攻佔了Kozinka、Glotove、Gora-Podil，目前正在爭奪Greyvoron的控制權。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9LeWl2SW5kZXBlbmRlbnQvc3RhdHVzLzE2NjA2NDIwMjQxNzE3NDUyODI\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/KyivIndependent/status/1660642024171745282\">https://twitter.com/KyivIndependent/status/1660642024171745282</a><br/>\r\n基輔獨立報報導，烏克蘭的一名軍事情報發言人承認了與烏克蘭當局合作的俄羅斯抵抗組織在別爾哥羅德地區進行的軍事行動。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n有網友上傳了相關影片：<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9iYXlyYWt0YXJfMWxvdmUvc3RhdHVzLzE2NjA1NjE4ODQ4OTY5NTIzMjI_dD1DSGxxa2hyZ2xteEEycjN1M09XUkJ3JnM9MTk\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/bayraktar_1love/status/1660561884896952322?t=CHlqkhrglmxA2r3u3OWRBw&amp;s=19\">https://twitter.com/bayraktar_1love/status/1660561884896952322?t=CHlqkhrglmxA2r3u3OWRBw&amp;s=19</a><br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9iYXlyYWt0YXJfMWxvdmUvc3RhdHVzLzE2NjA1NjczNjQ3NjM2MzU3MTI_dD15b28zdURSMGpsaWQybjJLVkpSZzRnJnM9MTk\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/bayraktar_1love/status/1660567364763635712?t=yoo3uDR0jlid2n2KVJRg4g&amp;s=19\">https://twitter.com/bayraktar_1love/status/1660567364763635712?t=yoo3uDR0jlid2n2KVJRg4g&amp;s=19</a><br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9HaXJraW5HaXJraW4vc3RhdHVzLzE2NjA2MDU2ODkyNDMzMzY3MDQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/GirkinGirkin/status/1660605689243336704\">https://twitter.com/GirkinGirkin/status/1660605689243336704</a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n可能有人不知道所以說明一下：<br/>\r\n自由俄羅斯軍團是由投誠的俄軍所組成的隸屬於烏克蘭當局的武裝部隊。<br/>\r\n俄羅斯志願軍團是由反對普特勒的俄國民主抵抗組織組成的外國志願軍。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
